OL,3,CMan admits killing 'kind and caring'
OL,4,Cdad in 'hit and run' crash
OL,6,FA man has admitted knocking down and
OL,7,Fkilling a 'kind and caring' dad in a
OL,8,F'hit-and-run'.
OL,10,FPedestrian Andy Morris, 46, was struck
OL,11,Fby a car on the A6 Buxton Road in
OL,12,FGreat Moor, Stockport in the early
OL,13,Fhours of 18 February 2023.
OL,15,FHe spent almost a month in hospital
OL,16,Fbut died of his injuries on 14 March.
OL,18,FLouie Baguley, 37, was arrested and
OL,19,Fcharged with causing death by
OL,20,Fdangerous driving, which he denied.
