OL,6,FHowever, on the day his trial was due
OL,7,Fto get underway at Manchester's
OL,8,FMinshull Street Crown Court on Monday
OL,9,F(28 April), he changed his plea to
OL,10,Fguilty.
OL,12,FBaguley, from Cheadle, had already
OL,13,Fadmitted perverting the course of
OL,14,Fjustice.
OL,16,FJudge Joanne Woodward told him a
OL,17,Fcustodial sentence was 'inevitable.'
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
