OL,3,CMan admits killing 'kind and caring'
OL,4,Cdad in 'hit and run' crash
OL,6,FMichael Goldwater, defending, said:
OL,7,F"He realises that a significant
OL,8,Fcustodial sentence is the only
OL,9,Fpossible outcome.
OL,11,F"He's married, he has a child, he has
OL,12,Fa grandchild, he's in employment and
OL,13,Fthe court would benefit from a more
OL,14,Fdetailed knowledge of his background
OL,15,Fand circumstances before determining
OL,16,Fthe appropriate sentence."
OL,18,FThe judge ordered a pre-sentence
OL,19,Freport and remanded him into custody
OL,20,Fahead of his sentencing until 10 July.
