OL,6,FShe said he was a man of "previous
OL,7,Fgood character" and that there was
OL,8,F"much to be said by the way of
OL,9,Fpersonal mitigation."
OL,11,F"This is an extremely serious offence"
OL,12,Fshe added.
OL,14,F"Not only by the standard of your
OL,15,Fdriving, but the consequence of the
OL,16,Fstandard of your driving. A custodial
OL,17,Fsentence is inevitable."
