OL,6,FIn a tribute issued following his
OL,7,Fdeath, Mr Morris' family said: "In
OL,8,Floving memory of Andy, who was sadly
OL,9,Ftaken away too soon. Andy was a loving
OL,10,Ffather, son, brother and friend.
OL,12,F"Our hearts will be forever broken not
OL,13,Fhaving you in our lives. Your
OL,14,Finfectious laugh, joke telling,
OL,15,Fsinging (well, debatable singing that
OL,16,Fis!) and magic tricks will forever be
OL,17,Fwith us all.
